Package eu.smartdatalake.simsearch.service

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SimSearchController
    Controller that handles all HTTP requests to the RESTful web service.
    SimSearchServiceApplication
    Instantiates a Spring boot application with default configurations.
    SimSearchServiceLauncher
    Entry point to the RESTful web service that invokes a Spring boot application.
    SpringFoxConfig
    Configuration of Swagger using a Docket bean for exposing the documentation of the REST API requests supported by the back-end service.
